name: Jump Out (CP Verlag)
overview: In this puzzle game you jump the color of your opponent as though you were playing checkers\droughts. If you can jump multiple times the better! Jump more than your oppenent and you win! Many starting scenarios to choose from. Published in Magic Disk 64 1991/07, Magic Disk 64 GE 1992/1, and also in Abo Disk #4.
